Actually, Go ahead, Piss him off! Then I'll have a reason to hunt you!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I see you now have the 10th rank. Good. now, you can go to the area ranked navis have to themselves if you can find it. but i doubt they will be there yet. come back later and i will have your next objective.

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Ok, what was it you needed?

properties.property:
Im looking to take out the Mafia.
Now i know by your expression that it seems impossible. members are everywhere. However, not everyone here is in with the mob. I need you to speak to the Ranked Navis.

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Aren't they like... super elusive to find though?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Yes, but i hear Rank 10 is looking to leave the game. If you could get your hands on that rank 10, you SHOULD be able to speak with any of the other ranked navis, and help coordinate an attack against the mafia.

properties.property:
WHOA!!!!!!
Whoa whoa whoa HOLD ON. you want ME to become a ranked navi?!

property.value: Hey, on one hand, you get to help shut down a massive criminal organization, which will mean compensation. Further, being a ranked navi is a sign of power. Navis that would pay you no mind will show you some respect, EVEN some of the mafia members. Go find rank 10, do whatever it takes to gain his rank, and come back to me. Got it?
